'''阿努拉德普勒'''（{{lang-pi|Anurādhapura}}，[[僧伽罗语|僧伽罗语]]：{{Unicode|අනුරාධපුරය }}，[[泰米爾文|泰米爾文]]：{{Unicode|அனுராதபுரம்}}），又譯為'''阿努拉達普拉'''，'''阿㝹羅陀補羅'''（{{標音|字=㝹|注音=ㄋㄡˊ|拼音=nou2}}），'''阿㝹羅陀城'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://buddhaspace.org/dict/fk/data/%25E5%2583%25A7%25E4%25BC%25BD%25E8%259C%259C%25E5%25A4%259A.html|title=僧伽蜜多|website=佛光大辭典|editor=慈怡法師|access-date=2020-05-28|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003024740/http://buddhaspace.org/dict/fk/data/%25E5%2583%25A7%25E4%25BC%25BD%25E8%259C%259C%25E5%25A4%259A.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dzj520.com/cidian/cidian1/5.html|title=阿㝹罗陀补罗|website=佛学大词典|accessdate=2020-05-28|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003024741/http://www.dzj520.com/cidian/cidian1/5.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[阿努拉德普勒區|阿努拉德普勒區]]的首府，為[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]的傳統首都，它以保存了許多古代斯里蘭卡文化及古蹟而聞名於世。<Ref>
{{cite book|url=https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780192800947.001.0001/acref-9780192800947-e-552|title=The Concise Oxford Dictionary of World Religions|first=John|last=Bowker|date=2003-01-01|publisher=Oxford University Press|via=www.oxfordreference.com|doi=10.1093/acref/9780192800947.001.0001/acref-9780192800947-e-552|access-date=2020-05-29|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003024742/https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780192800947.001.0001/acref-9780192800947-e-552|dead-url=no}}
</ref>

它從[[公元|公元]]前437年開始，一直到公元1017年，都是斯里蘭卡的首都。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780195076189.001.0001/acref-9780195076189-e-0022|title=The Oxford Companion to Archaeology|first=Robin A. E.|last=Coningham|date=1996-05-29|publisher=Oxford University Press|via=www.oxfordreference.com|doi=10.1093/acref/9780195076189.001.0001/acref-9780195076189-e-0022|access-date=2020-05-29|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118055146/https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780195076189.001.0001/acref-9780195076189-e-0022|dead-url=no}}</ref>它的古城被指定為聯合國[[世界遺產|世界遺產]]。

